question: Provide me with a summary ranking of the different user_id process ownership classification in the system_mods_power_consumption dataset. Rank the user_ids by the sum of total power consumed within the user_id, in descending order. Provide me with the ranking number as well as the sum total power consumed so I can have a sense of scale.
sql: select user_id, sum(total_power_consumption) as total_power_consumption, rank() over (order by sum(total_power_consumption) desc )as rnk from reporting.system_mods_power_consumption group by user_id;
